OL,3,CNew arrest as investigations continue
OL,4,Cat Cheshire religious group
OL,6,FCheshire Police have made an 11th
OL,7,Farrest in their investigation of
OL,8,Fpeople linked to the Crewe-based
OL,9,FAhmadi Religion of Peace and Light.
OL,11,FProperties linked to the religious
OL,12,Fgroup were raided at the end of last
OL,13,Fmonth following allegations of sexual
OL,14,Fabuse, forced marriage and people
OL,15,Ftrafficking.
OL,17,FAll of the offences are reported to
OL,18,Fhave taken place in 2023 and involved
OL,19,Fone victim, a woman, who was a member
OL,20,Fof the group at the time the offences
OL,21,Foccurred.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
