OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778332261
OL,3,CNew arrest as investigations continue
OL,4,Cat Cheshire religious group
OL,6,FInitially six men and three women were
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of offences
OL,8,Fincluding rape, human trafficking,
OL,9,Fmodern slavery, sexual assault and
OL,10,Fforced marriage offences.
OL,12,FThey have since been released on
OL,13,Fconditional bail.
OL,15,FAn 11th suspect, a 48-year-old British
OL,16,Fnational, was held on suspicion of
OL,17,Fhuman trafficking offences on Thursday
OL,18,F7 May at an address in Crewe.
OL,20,FHe has since been released on
OL,21,Fconditional bail.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
