OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778332261
OL,3,CNew arrest as investigations continue
OL,4,Cat Cheshire religious group
OL,6,FIn addition, officers have also
OL,7,Fapplied for Slavery and Trafficking
OL,8,FRisk Order against the man which is
OL,9,Fset to be heard in court next week.
OL,11,FSuperintendent Adam Waller, Head of
OL,12,Fthe Major Crime Directorate at
OL,13,FCheshire Constabulary, said: "This
OL,14,Finvestigation is still very much
OL,15,Factive and remains at a fast past
OL,17,F"While all the suspects we have
OL,18,Farrested are members of the group, as
OL,19,Fwe have stated from the beginning,
OL,20,Fthis is not an investigation into the
OL,21,Freligion.
OL,26,@uD@^OUyD@AOU
