OL,3,CNew arrest as investigations continue
OL,4,Cat Cheshire religious group
OL,6,FOur investigation solely focuses on
OL,7,Fthe serious allegations which have
OL,8,Fbeen reported to us.
OL,10,F"With that in mind, I'd also remind
OL,11,Feveryone that this remains a live
OL,12,Finvestigation which will take some
OL,13,Ftime, and I would ask that people do
OL,14,Fnot speculate while the case remains
OL,15,Fongoing."
